# Project Structure

- **Source**: `src/` — React app (main.jsx, App.jsx, components, index.css)
- **Data**: `public/site.json` — content, projects, patents, press, publications (loaded at runtime)
- **Assets**: `public/timo_1.png`, `public/work-images/` — served at root
- **Build**: `npm run build` (Vite) → `dist/`
- **Edit content** in `public/site.json`
- **Edit styles** in `src/index.css`
- **Do not** edit `dist/` — it is overwritten on each build

## Key paths

- `public/site.json` — content, projects, patents, press, publications
- `public/timo_1.png` — nav photo
- `public/work-images/*.png` — project images
- `src/components/` — Nav, AboutSection, PrinciplesSection, WorksSection, WorkDetail, PatentsSection, PressSection, TalksSection, ArticlesSection
- `src/utils/imageMap.js` — IMAGE_FILENAME_MAP, getProjectImageUrl, formatProjectTitle
